tel_Guest_Room_5.jpg</Url><Width>312</Width><Height>235</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/PAIZ-91hotel_Guest_Room_5_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/7/PAIZ-91hotel_Other_1.jpg</Url><Width>312</Width><Height>235</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/PAIZ-91hotel_Other_1_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Pai, Mae Hong Son, a small town lying along the Pai River near the Myanmar border nestled within a stunning green mountain range. If you are looking for relaxation, venture into town for excellent market place which brings colorful crowds of villagers, or take a more adventure approach, The Montis Resort is the place for you.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The resort is located in the heart of Pai making it to perfect base from which to explore the entire region.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Each of our spacious villas is located in 49 sqm of luxurious living space with their own terrace, enabling you to enjoy the stunning mountain views around Pai. They are five type of villa : Hippo, Widebeest, Zebra, Ostrich and Hyena. Each room is taestfully decorated according to its designated animal name.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>The resort is an authentic Northen-Thai Style, built in harmony with the unspoiled forested backdrop.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>Enjoy a wide variety of both Thai and Western cuisine in our five star restaurant, whilst dining in luxurious surroundings. Top chefs deliver high quality dishes from all around the globe, and food is served by our highly trained catering staff. The restaurant includes a fully-stocked drinks bar and wonderful views.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>Montis Restaurant - The Lobby is set in a spacious area with high wooden ceilings and stylised lighting. The warm interiors emanate an ambience and a relaxing sense of well-being for the weary traveller. The lobby includes panoramic views and comfortable seating, as well as a relaxing water feature.    Montis Cafe - Enjoying partaking of the refreshments in our international standard café? There is a selection of the finest aromatic coffee available in a variety of blends. There are also a variety of teas and other light refreshments available. The café is located in highly stylised surroundings with excellent views and state of the art furniture in which to unwind.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>CoffeeTeaMaker</Code><Text>Tea and Coffee maker</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantAirconditioned</Code><Text>Restaurant Air-Condit